Cyrus SASL OAuth2/OIDC Plugin Authors
====================================

Primary Author:
  Stephane Benoit <stefb@wizzz.net>

Contributors:
  j

Special Thanks:
  - OpenIDC community for liboauth2
  - Cyrus SASL team for the SASL framework
  - Authentik team for OIDC implementation reference

This plugin was developed to provide native OAuth2/OpenID Connect support
for SASL-enabled mail servers, replacing custom fallback mechanisms with
a comprehensive liboauth2-based solution.